  "texts": [
    "To guide ants not carrying food, we specified that they should navigate toward food using the highest pheromone concentration.",
    "Their ability to find food sources when pheromone trails were present was clearly improved in this way.",
    "However, inconsistencies in following pheromone gradients persisted.",
    "In the absence of pheromones or nest scents, ants tended to remain near the nest, exhibiting inefficient exploration behaviors.",
    "By distinguishing between the states of carrying and not carrying food, we enhanced the ants' foraging efficiency when environmental cues were available."
  ],
